  "detailed_description": "Ukhar is a 2D action adventure game set in a sword and sorcery world.<br>After exhausting the resources of Ka'ur's realm, the ambitious necromancer Kairus, is conducting his<br>raider army towards the city of Avendia.<br>Devastating everything upon their path, they burn Ukhar's camp and kidnap the lovely Neia.<br><br>Push back your limits and become stronger every level by facing all kinds of<br>monstrous creatures.<br>But above all ... help the young barbarian to defeat his enemies and save the beloved Neia,<br>from Kairus' grasp.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Sword and sorcery world.<br></li><li>Fight your enemies with a variety of weapons.<br></li><li>Hand-drawn cutscene art narrate the story segments.<br></li><li>22 levels spread over 7 different places.<br></li><li>Awe-inspiring soundtrack selected from Purple Planet.</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "Ukhar is a 2D action adventure game set in a sword and sorcery world.<br>After exhausting the resources of Ka'ur's realm, the ambitious necromancer Kairus, is conducting his<br>raider army towards the city of Avendia.<br>Devastating everything upon their path, they burn Ukhar's camp and kidnap the lovely Neia.<br><br>Push back your limits and become stronger every level by facing all kinds of<br>monstrous creatures.<br>But above all ... help the young barbarian to defeat his enemies and save the beloved Neia,<br>from Kairus' grasp.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Sword and sorcery world.<br></li><li>Fight your enemies with a variety of weapons.<br></li><li>Hand-drawn cutscene art narrate the story segments.<br></li><li>22 levels spread over 7 different places.<br></li><li>Awe-inspiring soundtrack selected from Purple Planet.</li></ul>",
